{"tid":530660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳撤銷「二線關」促特區一體化　國務院：要加強粵港邊界管控","createTime":"2018-01-16T03:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T04:54:01.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9602c3d163561f9022bac4fa2ec4b81270e8d24a","tid":530660,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"國務院今日發布通知，同意撤銷深圳經濟特區管理線，實施深圳全市域統一的城鄉規劃建設管理。通知又表示，要進一步加強粵港邊界一線管控，強化基礎設施建設，確保粵港邊界持續穩定。<br />\n<br />\n國務院通知，為促進深圳經濟特區一體化發展，結合特區建設發展面臨的新形勢、新使命、新任務，同意撤銷深圳經濟特區管理線，以進一步優化城市功能佈局，完善交通基礎設施，實現更高質量的城市化。深圳經濟特區管理線撤銷後，要進一步加强粵港邊界一線管控，強化基礎設施建設，確保粵港邊界持續穩定。<br />\n<br />\n深圳特區管理線（即「二線」）設立於1982年6月，在深圳市內，劃分經濟特區與非特區。當時的經濟特區區域，只包括羅湖、福田、南山及鹽田四個區域。這條管理線東起大鵬灣畔背仔角，西到南頭安樂村，全長84.6公里，由2.8米高的鐵絲網和沿途的巡邏公路構成，是一道「二線關」。管理線上設有多個檢查站。至於「一線」，則指粵港粵澳邊界線。<br />\n<br />\n2010年7月1日，國務院批准將寶安區和龍崗區劃入經濟特區，特區範圍擴大到深圳全市，實現關內外一體化，但「二線關」仍然存在。隨著深圳市發展，二線關查驗的功能逐漸弱化。2014年7月，深圳特區檢查站所有官兵被撤走，「二線關」名存實亡，只剩下關口的建築和車檢通道等。2015年起，深圳市開始清拆二線關，到2017年底，所有二線關已經全部拆除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7-%E4%BA%8C%E7%B7%9A%E9%97%9C-%E4%BF%83%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E4%B8%80%E9%AB%94%E5%8C%96-%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2-%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E9%82%8A%E7%95%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2597%259C-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%258C%2596-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=KuaNbBkNI42Yn%2Fk0NiwpP7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5aaf991b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7-%25E4%25BA%258C%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2597%259C-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258D%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%258C%2596-%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=f2b10e96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7-%E4%BA%8C%E7%B7%9A%E9%97%9C-%E4%BF%83%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E4%B8%80%E9%AB%94%E5%8C%96-%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2-%E8%A6%81%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E7%B2%B5%E6%B8%AF%E9%82%8A%E7%95%8C%E7%AE%A1%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"968ac79583396d9266e81e32932caef240711a0b","tid":530660,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"正式成為深港市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ced7710417bf7dcc27a93469d755c821e17609","tid":530660,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"劇本快到,遲下右軚轉左軚,人民幣取代港幣<br />\n<br />\n毫冇意外,2040年香港變到同支那一模一樣,2047正式一國一制<br />\n<br />\n正如李光耀話到左2047你覺得香港仲會同支那有分別嗎？<br />\n<br />\n大家都係努力諗辦法移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a756086e610f37cbce5dc7f7803199a4e5bc50d","tid":530660,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為係回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係一早冇咗咩？"},{"pid":"3d3c385ad1e562771bfec8dc62db2cb700408fd2","tid":530660,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a756086e610f37cbce5dc7f7803199a4e5bc50d","tid":530660,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為係回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係一早冇咗咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"你以為冇其實暗中進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貪曾年代已經放風要整港深大都會,將2個城市合而為一都算,仲話可以超越東京紐約,笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7681d08d504e7ced345c459ef5be190468dc0f2","tid":530660,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"二線係深圳境內姐，<br />\n個聲明係話要加強一線控制wor"},{"pid":"cf27cf4ad8d64176893b87ae4a84d697c2157836","tid":530660,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a021fabf343ff81dbf7772147dd3ea0035ff20bb","tid":530660,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d3c385ad1e562771bfec8dc62db2cb700408fd2","tid":530660,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a756086e610f37cbce5dc7f7803199a4e5bc50d","tid":530660,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為係回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係一早冇咗咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"你以為冇其實暗中進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貪曾年代已經放風要整港深大都會,將2個城市合而為一都算,仲話可以超越東京紐約,笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"二線關呀，關香港咩事<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/ftp/News/20150328/_Tch1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20150328%2F_Tch1.jpg&h=0cdc966b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}